Package: Rwasmtime
Type: Package
Title: Embed 'Wasmtime' WebAssembly Runtimes in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure", email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Bytecode Alliance", role = "cph", comment = "Wasmtime project and Rust crate"),
    person("Hiroaki", "Yutani", role = "cph", comment = "savvy R/Rust interface inspiration")
  )
Description: Pipe-first R API scaffold for embedding the 'Wasmtime' WebAssembly
    runtime through a Rust core and a thin 'savvy' R adapter. The intended
    implementation exposes low-level module, component, linker, store, memory,
    asynchronous job, AOT artifact, WASI sandbox, and host-callback operations,
    plus higher-level sandbox/app composition and REPL-like protocols for guests
    such as webR.
